Download TIGER shapes for Urban Area

Source: R/uac.R
tt_uac.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Urban Area

Usage

tt_uac(year = 2021)

Arguments

year

Integer year. Required. Years < 2012 are not currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

tt_uac()
